---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'healthcare-system', text: 'Healthcare System', level: 2 },
  { id: 'visa-requirements', text: 'Visa Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'insurance-requirements', text: 'Insurance Requirements', level: 2 },
  { id: 'recommended-providers', text: 'Recommended Providers', level: 2 },
  { id: 'costs', text: 'Expected Costs', level: 2 },
  { id: 'scenarios', text: 'Real-World Scenarios', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'Common Questions', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Kazakhstan Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/kazakhstan/insurance' },
  { title: 'Insurance for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors' },
  { title: 'Georgia for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/georgia' },
  { title: 'Turkey for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/turkey' },
  { title: 'UAE for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/uae' },
];

const providerColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'entryAge', header: 'Max Entry Age' },
  { key: 'renewal', header: 'Renewal' },
  { key: 'monthlyFrom', header: 'From (65-69)' },
  { key: 'kazakhstanFit', header: 'Kazakhstan Fit' },
];

const providerRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'KZT$225,000-321,400/mo', kazakhstanFit: 'Excellent' },
  { provider: 'BUPA Global', entryAge: '79', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'KZT$263,250-376,040/mo', kazakhstanFit: 'Excellent' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'KZT$202,500-289,260/mo', kazakhstanFit: 'Very Good' },
  { provider: 'Now Health', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'KZT$188,250-268,815/mo', kazakhstanFit: 'Very Good' },
  { provider: 'Local (Kazakh Insurance)', entryAge: '60', renewal: 'Varies', monthlyFrom: 'KZT$30,000-80,000/mo', kazakhstanFit: 'Limited' },
];

const costColumns = [
  { key: 'category', header: 'Expense' },
  { key: 'monthly', header: 'Monthly' },
  { key: 'annual', header: 'Annual' },
];

const costRows = [
  { category: 'International Insurance (65-69)', monthly: 'KZT$202,500-321,400', annual: 'KZT$2.43M-3.86M' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (70-74)', monthly: 'KZT$277,800-428,550', annual: 'KZT$3.33M-5.14M' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (75-79)', monthly: 'KZT$373,500-575,100', annual: 'KZT$4.48M-6.9M' },
  { category: 'Private Hospital Visit', monthly: 'KZT$15,000-40,000/visit', annual: 'Affordable' },
  { category: 'Private Hospital Stay', monthly: 'KZT$80,000-200,000/day', annual: 'Per incident' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Health Insurance for Seniors in Kazakhstan 2026 | Retirement Guide"
  description="Guide to health insurance for seniors in Kazakhstan. Central Asian hub, Almaty mountains, affordable living, and coverage for expats 65+."
  headline="Health Insurance for Seniors in Kazakhstan"
  subheadline="Kazakhstan offers Central Asian grandeur, Almaty mountain beauty, modern cities, affordable living, and oil-funded development—the region's most accessible and developed country for adventurous retirees."
  heroImage="/images/countries/kazakhstan-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Senior Plans →"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Why Seniors Choose Kazakhstan</h2>
  <p>
    Kazakhstan offers Central Asia's most developed infrastructure, stunning Almaty mountains, modern Astana architecture, affordable living, and fascinating Silk Road history. For adventurous retirees seeking exotic experience with reasonable comfort, Kazakhstan provides unique Eurasian crossroads.
  </p>

  <p>
    Almaty has best healthcare and mountain lifestyle. Astana (Nur-Sultan) is futuristic capital. Shymkent offers southern warmth. Most expats choose Almaty for healthcare, culture, and natural beauty. Healthcare is improving with oil investment.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Key Facts for Seniors</h3>
    <ul class="text-primary-800 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Improving; Turkey/Dubai backup available</li>
      <li><strong>Language:</strong> Kazakh, Russian widely spoken</li>
      <li><strong>Cost of Living:</strong> KZT$300,000-600,000/month (~$665-1,330 USD); affordable</li>
      <li><strong>Climate:</strong> Continental; cold winters; pleasant summers</li>
      <li><strong>Character:</strong> Modern; diverse; developing</li>
      <li><strong>Visa:</strong> Visa-free for many nationalities</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="healthcare-system">Kazakhstan Healthcare System</h2>
  <p>
    Kazakhstan healthcare is improving—National Research Medical Center and private hospitals in Almaty provide modern care. Many doctors trained in Russia or Turkey. Complex cases may need Istanbul (4-hour flight) or Dubai. Oil investment funding healthcare development.
  </p>

  <p>
    Private healthcare in Almaty/Astana is good and affordable. Public system variable. International insurance with Turkey/Dubai coverage recommended for comprehensive access.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-2">Improving Healthcare</h3>
    <p class="text-amber-800 mb-0">
      Kazakhstan healthcare is improving with oil investment. Almaty has good private options. Istanbul and Dubai provide backup for complex cases. Include Turkey/UAE in insurance coverage. Better than most Central Asian neighbors.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="visa-requirements">Visa Options for Seniors</h2>
  <p>
    Kazakhstan has accessible visa policies:
  </p>

  <h3>Visa-Free Entry</h3>
  <p>
    30-day visa-free for many nationalities including US, EU, UK. Simple entry.
  </p>

  <h3>Electronic Visa</h3>
  <p>
    For longer stays or nationalities not covered by visa-free. Simple online process.
  </p>

  <h3>Residence Permit</h3>
  <p>
    For stays over 30 days. Various categories. Apply through migration service.
  </p>

  <h3>Investment/Business Visa</h3>
  <p>
    For business activities. Kazakhstan encouraging foreign investment.
  </p>

  <h2 id="insurance-requirements">Insurance Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance requirements for Kazakhstan:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Entry:</strong> Travel insurance recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Residence:</strong> Health insurance recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Practical:</strong> International coverage recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Regional:</strong> Turkey/UAE coverage helpful</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for Kazakhstan</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
      International insurance with Turkey/UAE coverage recommended. Almaty private care handles most needs. Regional hubs provide specialist backup. Good combination of local improving care and international access.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="recommended-providers">Recommended Insurance Providers</h2>
  <p>
    For seniors in Kazakhstan, regional coverage important:
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={providerColumns} rows={providerRows} />

  <h3>Why These Providers Work for Kazakhstan</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cigna Global:</strong> Strong regional network, Turkey access</li>
    <li><strong>BUPA Global:</strong> Highest entry age (79), comprehensive</li>
    <li><strong>Istanbul access:</strong> Regional medical hub</li>
    <li><strong>Improving locally:</strong> Almaty care getting better</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Get Personalized Senior Quotes</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Compare coverage for Kazakhstan.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/bupa-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get BUPA Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="costs">Expected Insurance Costs</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance costs for Kazakhstan (KZT ~450 to USD):
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

  <h3>Cost-Saving Strategies</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Almaty base:</strong> Best local healthcare</li>
    <li><strong>High deductible:</strong> Local care affordable</li>
    <li><strong>Turkey network:</strong> Use for complex care</li>
    <li><strong>Regional plans:</strong> Central Asia/Middle East focused</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="scenarios">Real-World Scenarios</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 1: Adventure Retiree, 67</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $2,200/month pension. Long-stay visa. Almaty.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with CIS/Turkey coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~KZT$240,000/month (~$535). Mountain lifestyle; regional backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 2: Russian-Speaker, 70</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $2,800/month income. Residence permit. Almaty.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> BUPA Global with CIS coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~KZT$300,000/month (~$665). Language ease; comprehensive backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 3: Oil Industry Connection, 66</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $3,500/month pension. Business visa. Astana.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Allianz Care with Dubai coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~KZT$220,000/month (~$490). Industry connection; global access.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Do I need Russian?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Very helpful—Russian widely spoken, more so than Kazakh in cities. English limited outside business/tourism. Healthcare often in Russian. Learning Russian opens more opportunities. Kazakh growing but Russian remains lingua franca.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is Kazakhstan safe?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Generally safe—low crime for region. Politically stable (authoritarian but functioning). Some protests occasionally. Tourist areas very safe. Normal precautions apply. Safer than many emerging market destinations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What's Almaty like?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Attractive—set against Tian Shan mountains. Good restaurants, culture, parks. Soviet architecture mixed with modern. Ski resorts nearby. Pleasant in summer. Cold winters (-10 to -20°C). Green and relatively clean. Best quality of life in Central Asia.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Why choose Kazakhstan over neighbors?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Most developed in Central Asia—better infrastructure, healthcare, internet. Oil wealth funds development. More accessible visa policy. Safer than Kyrgyzstan/Uzbekistan alternatives. Closer to modern standards while still exotic.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Ready to Compare Options?</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Get quotes from providers for Kazakhstan coverage.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/allianz-care" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide is for informational purposes only. Insurance requirements, visa regulations, and healthcare access rules change regularly. Always verify current requirements with Kazakhstan authorities and consult with a licensed insurance professional.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
